                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       Good Morning
      Hello It's Thursday , July 10 , 2008                    
	Workshop    A workshop on improving presentation skills at Hotel Hindustan International, 10am to 6pm.    
	Lecture    A session of lectures organised by Centre for Studies in Dance Forms of Bengal at Kavijanani Sarada Kaksha, Emerald Bower campus, 1pm.    
	Theatre    A dramatised play reading of The Marriage Play by Edward Albee at Padatik, 7pm.     Inauguration of Eastern Science Drama Competition 2008 at Birla Industrial and Technological Museum, 10.30am.    
	Fashion    Exhibition of textiles and artefacts of Orissa and Bengal at Artisana, 13 Chowringhee Terrace, 11am to 7pm.    
	Art watch    Recent works by Sandip Roy at Akar Prakar, 2pm to 7pm.    La terre at Gallery Nakshatra, 2/1 Outram Street, noon to 7pm.     The Magic of Monochrome, a group show of drawings and paintings, at Gandhara Art Gallery, 1pm to 7pm.    Springs in White at Rabindranath Tagore Centre, 11am to 6pm.     Tasveer, photos by Swapan Nayak and Tim Hall, at Seagull Arts and Media Resource Centre, 6pm.    Nakshi Kantha of Bengal at Birla Academy of Art and Culture, 3pm to 8pm.                                                                                                                                                                 
